'''喬·莱西特'''（'''Joe Lycett'''，{{bd|1988年|7月5日}}）是[[英國|英國]]的一位喜劇演員<ref>{{cite web|title=Instagram Post by close friend and fellow comedian, Aisling Bea|url=https://instagram.com/p/4xSyFyv1-d/|access-date=2016-05-07|archive-date=2016-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419074449/https://www.instagram.com/p/4xSyFyv1-d/}}</ref>。他主持有多檔喜劇節目，包括[[BBC_One|BBC One]]的[[Epic_Win|Epic Win]]。莱西特是一位[[雙性戀|雙性戀]]者<ref>{{cite web|title=TV comic Joe Lycett on his epic win and sexuality|url=http://www.sundaymercury.net/news/midlands-news/2011/08/14/tv-comic-joe-lycett-on-his-epic-win-and-sexuality-66331-29230273/}}</ref>。2020年3月1日，他宣布將自己的正式名字改為Hugo Boss，以抗議[[Hugo_Boss|同名公司]]發送公開信要求小企業和慈善機構停用「boss」一詞<ref name="HugoBBC">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-51703859|title=Joe Lycett: Comedian changes his name to Hugo Boss|publisher=BBC|date=2 March 2020|accessdate=2 March 2020|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220125854/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-51703859}}</ref>。

